room_title: Escape room "Poindexter's Pad" by Brainstorm Escape Room Bonita Springs in Fort Myers
room_description:
Tired of trying to prove to the Math and Science nerds that you are just as smart as they are you accept their challenge to escape from their hangout. They have hidden clues and puzzles to help you find the exit code. You have 60 minutes to prove you have what it takes to finally be accepted as their equal.
This room contains ADVANCED math.
